{"tid":1548651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陰謀論：警隊被清算，武警/解放軍進場","createTime":"2019-09-07T05:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T08:45:13.000Z","uid":160023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b55ab6697165180c1017780fd6ae22ab54f2582e","tid":1548651,"uid":160023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"依家班狗做左咁多衰野，佢地以為冇人知，政府其實暗地裡記錄低晒。等到臨近10.1就宣佈清算，但由於大部分狗都被停職，無法維持社會治安同秩序，因此政府請求武警/解放軍協助。<br />\n<br />\n清算警隊可以令民怨進一步降低，10.1出黎嘅人就會減少。而武警/解放軍就可以名正言順在港執法，到時就可以借機以武力鎮懾令10.1遊行難產。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，就算佢地咁樣做我都唔會驚嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n一日未滿足到，大家都要堅持住呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7343579a0f8e220770a868697084e00001ccd85a","tid":1548651,"uid":193056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"共產黨唯一可以嬴返少少民心既方法就係派解放軍處決屠殺3萬警隊"},{"pid":"4b2e60fb7fce04ca5ccd86988dcf0b6e81b8d68f","tid":1548651,"uid":160023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7343579a0f8e220770a868697084e00001ccd85a","tid":1548651,"uid":193056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"共產黨唯一可以嬴返少少民心既方法就係派解放軍處決屠殺3萬警隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"正喎，快d黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fe9cedd8eeb922e59f3ea390784ab624091113","tid":1548651,"uid":171543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"清算黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}